- returns `"<first> <last>"` for `short === true` when nickname is absent
- returns `"<first> <last>"` for `short === true` when nickname is empty or whitespace-only
- returns `"<last>, <first>"` for `short === false` when nickname is absent
- returns `"<last>, <first>"` for `short === false` when nickname is empty or whitespace-only
- returns `"<last>, <first> (<nickname>)"` for `short === false` with a nickname
